videos.headline: Car's 44-yard run sets up Houston TD
videos.description: Mulbah Car sets up Houston at the 1-yard line after a 44-yard run and Bryson Smith finishes it off for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Car's 44-yard run sets up Houston TD) 2019/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: SMU strikes first with 15-yard TD
videos.description: Shane Buechele connects with James Proche down the middle for a 15-yard SMU touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (SMU strikes first with 15-yard TD) 2019/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jones reverses the field for 62-yard TD run
videos.description: Xavier Jones makes a tackler miss in the backfield, reverses up-field and takes it in for a 62-yard SMU touchdown.

videos.headline: Stevenson burns SMU defense for 75-yard TD
videos.description: Clayton Tune connects with Marquez Stevenson who goes 75 yards for the Houston touchdown.
